画出给定极坐标的点, 并求它们的笛卡尔坐标
(a) (sqrt(2), pi/4)
    x = r cos θ = sqrt(2) * sqrt(2) / 2 = 1
    y = r sin θ = sqrt(2) * sqrt(2) / 2 = 1

(b) (1, 0)
    x = r cos θ = 1
    y = r sin θ = 0

(c) (0, pi/2)
    x = r cos θ = 0
    y = r sin θ = 0

(d) (-sqrt(2), pi/4)
    x = r cos θ = -sqrt(2) * sqrt(2) / 2 = -1
    y = r sin θ = -sqrt(2) * sqrt(2) / 2 = -1

